Mr. Death: The Rise and Fall of Fred A. Leuchter, Jr.;;87;;100;;PG-13;;Documentary filmmaker Errol Morris investigates the case of a man who became an authority on capital punishment, but was discredited when he got involved on the wrong side of a court case. Leutcher, a meek man whose appearance belies his grim expertise, develops what he says is a more effective electric chair. Before long he's in demand from officials who want his opinions on other kinds of execution. But when called to aid the case of an accused Holocaust denier, Leutcher's problems begin.;;Documentary;;Errol Morris;;1999;;Fred A. Leuchter Jr.,Robert Jan Van Pelt,David Irving,Caroline Leuchter,James Roth,Shelly Shapiro,Suzanne Tabasky,Ernst ZÃ¼ndel,David Collins,Daniel Polsby,Robert Duerr;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mr_death_the_rise_and_fall_of_fred_a_leuchter_jr